description:
Beer-and-food expert Mandy Naglich journeys to London to experience the city’s storied food-and-pub scene.

From enjoying Thai food at a landmark pub to touring a local distillery, accompany Mandy as she discovers the people and places defining London’s food-and-pub scene in this episode of “Connected Journeys.”

Find out more about the places featured in Mandy’s story:
The Devonshire: https://www.devonshiresoho.co.uk/
The Churchill Arms: https://www.churchillarmskensington.co.uk/
Fuller’s Brewery: https://www.fullersbrewery.co.uk/
